## Scientific Content Attribution

This software implements physics simulations based on peer-reviewed scientific 
publications. While the code is MIT licensed, please cite the original sources
when using this software for research or educational purposes:

- Pearson, B.J., et al. (2018). "Measurements of slit-width effects in Young's 
  double-slit experiment." OSA Continuum, Optica. DOI: 10.1364/OSAC.1.000755

- Hong, C.K., Noh, T.G. (1998). "Two-photon double-slit interference experiment."
  J. Opt. Soc. Am. B 15, 1192-1197. DOI: 10.1364/JOSAB.15.001192
